    âپ…âپ…Hâ‚پ, Hâ‚‚âپ†, Hâ‚ƒâپ† = âٹ¥ := by
  simp_rw [commutator_eq_bot_iff_le_centralizer, commutator_le,
    mem_centralizer_iff_commutator_eq_one, â†گ commutatorElement_def] at h1 h2 âٹ¢
  intro x hx y hy z hz
